<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Thank You for Your Feedback</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      color: #007bff;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .form-data {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #dddddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .form-data p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Thank You <%= locals.fullName %>!</h1>
    <p>We have received your message and will get back to you as soon as possible. Below is a summary of the information
      you submitted:</p>

    <div class="form-data">
      <p><strong>Full Name:</strong>
        <%= locals.fullName %>
      </p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong>
        <%= locals.email %>
      </p>
      <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong>
        <%= locals.phoneNumber %>
      </p>
      <p><strong>Message:</strong>
        <%= locals.message %>
      </p>
    </div>

    <p>If you need to update your information or have any further questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br />IcodeU</p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>